B1%9F%E6%A8%82%E5%A3%AB-%E5%A4%A9%E6%9B%B8-%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E7%89%88-%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E5%B0%B1%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E7%AD%89%E9%87%8F%E5%88%91%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司前刑事檢控專員江樂士，與前高級檢控官，現任執業大律師張維新，昨日(10日)聯合出版「Sentencing in Hong Kong(第九修訂版)」，內容更新了法庭就暴動罪，以及破壞公眾秩序等罪行的量刑原則。本書著作自1994年首版發行，<ins>已獲律政司檢控科視為「天書」參考。</ins><br />\n<br />\n根據書中引言，書中除了摘錄法庭最近如何懲處破壞公眾秩序或觸犯暴動罪的罪犯，書中內容亦更新了同性肛交，牽涉販運瀕危動物罪行等的量刑標準。最新指引亦強調，「壓力」亦已不會接納為任何暴力案件的求情理由。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>終院法官李義在書中引言形容本著作是香港法院判刑的基石</ins>，書中提供客觀標準和原則，讓本港判刑決定符合法律框架。"},{"pid":"30c001ab1f21092ec9dd8453a3f0d11adc1030db","tid":2093543,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"呢條洋五毛一向奶共奶共發發聲<br />\n屢次美化警暴,對示威者抹黑<br />\n<br />\n律政司根本只會採用親共者的意見"},{"pid":"af7d58327cafa02d2d94e1136bac7ab9d09eea15","tid":2093543,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"乜唔係用Archbold㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pbookshop.com/archbold-hong-kong-2019-archbold2019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbookshop.com%2Farchbold-hong-kong-2019-archbold2019.html&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2ILQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=5b85e4e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pbookshop.com/archbold-hong-kong-2019-archbold2019.html</a><br />\n<br />\n// The Hon. Mr. Justice Bokhary continues as the Editor-in-Chief and Mr. Graham Harris QC as the General Editor.//<br />\n而且係包致金做總編<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ba0053fb07e460b5452ed99fbb9fb35ff8a0f7","tid":2093543,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7d58327cafa02d2d94e1136bac7ab9d09eea15","tid":2093543,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"乜唔係用Archbold㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 